Description

This is sales report of company, summarized by:

  • Sales Devision.
  • Day.
  • Day of week.
  • Day of month.
  • Month.
  • Year.

To reorder report just drag and drop table fields, add filters in the fiels buttons, change visualization type and select aggregation method.
